  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0584a3d7-5072-47c3-8c43-74a1c0d75f2b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8faf0f39-6002-43e2-b64b-25f8e7e9e9e0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-848efb15-49ab-4243-90fc-c7b17de0fb2e\">발목의 인대의 손상은 아주 빈번하게 발생합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-55a8cb74-f6e6-4644-a0b3-f85d8592e091\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0bb08b67-5f99-43d8-b887-44d4806a347a\">누구나 한 번 쯤은 발목을 삐끗해본 적이 있잖아요? ^^</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bb1d0674-0f02-42fe-b8ff-9a3093cf59dc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c6851675-f8ab-408a-8f4c-119be0d9144d\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ec594aa8-3f58-4bd8-bbd9-9591fdc087a7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b096e54a-c55c-4ddf-b4f8-a87206e814d1\">인대가 손상되는 것을 &#x27;염좌&#x27;라고 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d4ca9044-1412-40a1-9421-cda76fb56122\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4be9d414-1264-43fb-817e-1bf846bacb89\"><span class=\"__se-hash-tag\">#발목염좌</span></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a800717e-65f4-490f-8886-235fbaf21f41\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b52f30cc-9112-418d-8617-64409e711722\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e46d32b5-03bd-44e0-af92-261c9b3ea00d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c5d0faf7-5b56-4d69-98ca-d0614a6fc28f\">그래서 오늘은 발목 인대 염좌에 대해서 그림으로 간단히 설명을 해볼까 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1f82403b-3af5-49df-98e6-a21c9bb2bf88\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cd7a8a24-f3c9-4b65-8963-d644bdf0a0a8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a7f9f7df-0375-42ea-b5a2-a98a1edc524e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n\n                                <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module se-module-image __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\" \" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-a7f9f7df-0375-42ea-b5a2-a98a1edc524e\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/84aeba3abb2f6331.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/84aeba3abb2f6331.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/84aeba3abb2f6331.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"707\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                </a>                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7f3bd12d-79d3-4eda-afc1-eb7e57dd73ba\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cb1f35bb-68f6-47b5-ae2a-8afaecfcbbd7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-146e3831-dfb1-456f-85c8-a08de020de36\">대부분의 발목염좌는 위 그림 아래쪽에 나와있는 &#x27;내반&#x27;염좌입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-92a7dbbf-b3e9-47d9-9682-7d3ddd568fa8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-256bc4c3-f7c1-4c89-ba98-56afde833b5d\">그래서 바깥쪽 복숭아뼈 주변에 통증이 생기죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ecd2fe5b-002a-41c7-a843-c0e398a82583\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-94234d1c-ead7-412f-8faf-6cad252166bb\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-497eb94f-bc05-478d-b16e-f95dcc95d7c1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a494ce8b-63e2-474b-9864-b91d0edd5fa0\">붓고, 멍드는 정도와 걸을 때 아픈 정도를 보고서 얼마나 손상이 심한가를 판단합니다. 더불어 인대를 늘리는 동작을 해보고, 인대부위를 눌러봐서 얼마나 통증이 심한가 등도 판단의 기준이 될 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9ee35f65-18e7-4142-b847-7093cb9da6ef\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-47a82f37-94f6-4de1-8e3e-844dd8d09c7c\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c9061a32-0ccc-4d25-9ee7-1302d2721c4b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a19daeab-bbac-4e9d-812e-856b0755b9cb\">많이 붓고, 멍도 심하면서 3-4걸음 걷기도 힘들 정도로 걸을 때 통증이 심하다면 x-ray 촬영을 통해 뼈의 손상과 인대의 완전파열 등을 감별해야 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-966e1ac2-ff67-4856-adc7-7aa856d6ca1a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b8ace852-d798-4d98-9d2d-fd34e7e8a70f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5db216c4-6f04-4443-b830-0bc9a674c973\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0c40c7b4-f2fa-4e98-97fc-28b81191ec0e\">발목염좌를 치료하면서 통증이 줄어들게 되면 스스로 재활운동을 해줘야 빠른 회복과 재발방지가 가능합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e8a26e37-7a39-4642-8fa3-31f2c4cac8b1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-86fba15b-9653-4db7-a872-6f28a02b945b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1f495b37-858f-48d4-b33a-5170aab753af\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n\n                                <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module se-module-image __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\" \" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-1f495b37-858f-48d4-b33a-5170aab753af\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b58efedb16f2c7d0.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b58efedb16f2c7d0.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b58efedb16f2c7d0.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"707\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                </a>                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bdb8a52c-2033-494c-af7c-26368be7c231\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1101f3a3-78cd-4e93-8243-5579c557be7b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f148aac0-5185-4163-824f-e2a2940fdd47\">위 그림처럼 발목 주변의 근육과 힘줄을 강화시켜주는 운동을 하는거죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1e7c1e46-39c0-4ae3-bf51-31950f9d8927\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0654b393-e777-402b-a372-dfbe963e95f5\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-55a7243b-31c1-4745-b0fb-004de0a24140\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3b5dd4fc-1f29-4f87-b7e0-9c03ba465ab4\">예전에 발목을 삐끗한 이후로 주자 삐끗거린다 혹은 발목 염좌가 자주 발생한다고 하는 분들은 특히 위의 운동을 열심히 해주는 게 좋겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f80e3a5e-ffc1-4b4e-812f-a9dbe0975349\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cb753e38-1410-4814-b239-f9da78fc8b66\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dcc03a43-c7ac-4b7b-8fef-afc990072fef\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-325af8f9-0f0e-48de-866b-0ef5e5c06e03\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0d9084a9-7f30-4a6f-b865-aad834362333\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9a15a180-8094-436f-abbd-4403fdc284eb\">------ 이상  남성역 경희이수한의원이었습니다. ----------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-98a89453-fd69-4b0a-9283-56d0bbb7eb7c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4e4bd830-1be5-486e-b01c-73a2ed2031ae\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ec2a3ca1-275f-420d-88f9-86ad5e5b63dd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-655fc4cc-b43c-44ab-89e4-061193b391ec\"># 이수한의원 <span class=\"__se-hash-tag\">#남성역</span> 이수한의원 <span class=\"__se-hash-tag\">#남성역</span> 경희이수한의원</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-22942150-0018-45ae-bd4f-40976f89d799\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6877964b-2388-489e-aa97-0d880a09206f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-25ee0193-8e39-4cd0-bef9-282cb8f08ee6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5a245fa9-d943-4933-88e4-1b7272c8826f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b0141943-ef67-4d05-83b6-19010896f162\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n\n                                <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module se-module-image __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\" \" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-b0141943-ef67-4d05-83b6-19010896f162\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0184c8290a9fe435.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/i